OL,3,CCrews remain on site after fire on ship
OL,5,FA fire which broke out on a ship in
OL,6,FNewport has been contained, but crews
OL,7,Fremain on site, the fire service has
OL,8,Fconfirmed.
OL,10,FCrews were called to Newport Docks on
OL,11,FSunday morning after the fire broke
OL,12,Fout on the Nord Houston vessel.
OL,14,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,15,Fsaid crews remained on site on Sunday
OL,16,Fafternoon and will continue to do so
OL,17,Ffor the next 12-24 hours to ensure
OL,18,Fthere is no re-ignition.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
